results.description: Kaine is brought back to life by a wealthy businessman who wants to make him a contestant in The Great Game; A spider skeleton is found in the smoke stack.

results.description: Trainer comes out of his coma; Ben and Peter examine the Spider Skeleton.

results.title: Web of Carnage, Part 4 of 4: Inner Demons
results.description: Ben has been possessed by the Carnage symbiote.  Will he be able to control it?

results.title: Blood Brothers, Part 4 of 6: Leap of Faith
results.description: Ben has been beaten down by Hobgoblin.  Will he recover in time to save Peter from a similar fate.

results.title: Puppets
results.description: The ruthless Will o' the Wisp is back, more powerful than before, with his sights set on Spidey!  Only this Spidey's never even met the guy!  We smell trouble...! [per next issue box]

results.title: Free Will
results.description: Boy, things don't look so promising for Spidey winning this one, huh?  Dragon Man's loose... and this time, the big purple guy is under the control of Harrow's insidious device.  Can a severly outgunned Spider-Man count on his foe Will o' the Wisp to back him up?  Plus, a shocking development in the life of our now non-powered Mr. Parker. [per next issue box]

results.title: Little Deaths
results.description: What's wrong with Peter?  Can he survive this mysterious illness which has befallen him?  Well, here's a hint:  next issue opens with doctors declaring him dead!  Is the torch finally passing to Ben Reilly totally?  And what a lousy time for the monstrous Lizard to rear his ugly head again! [per next issue box]

results.title: Suicidal Tendencies
results.description: A creepy, moody tale focusing on the tortured psyche of Curt Connors!  What will the Doc do to change the planet he feels is falling apart?  What is this new Lizard, really, and what will he do when he finds his former alter ego?  And what can Spidey do about any of this? [per next issue box]

results.title: Sudden Sacrifices
results.description: Yesss sssir, he'ssss back!  The real Lizard has crawled into Spidey's life with a vengeance... and be very afraid, 'cause this time he's got a plan! [per next issue box]
